Barry Spatz,<br><br>
I'm sitting here with my morning coffee.  I just read the posts from last night on thread #20.<br><br>
Ed, recently asked you to please go away.  There are people here that are trying to &quot;do&quot; some important stuff.   Tom is right, stating that we are all different, viewpoints notwithstanding.<br><br>
